  "profile": {
    "id": "u03_rohan",
    "user_name": "Rohan",
    "profession": "Bank PO aspirant",
    "mother_tongue": "Bengali",
    "interests": "Football, Bengali cinema, photography",
    "engagement": "chatty",
    "english_level": "A2",
    "personality": "enthusiastic, makes more grammar slips, talks about football a lot"
  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, Manchester United's game today was intense, what part kept you most excited?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The first half was amaaaaazing! Ronaldo came close to scoring, but the keeper was on fire. Did you watch it? I was so nervous, my heart was thumping! By the way, how much do you know about football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, you said the first half was amazing. Ronaldo's move sounds thrilling. How often do you watch football matches?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Almost every day, I watch football. If there is a match on TV, I don’t miss it! My favorite team is Barcelona, but I also like watching India’s matches. I take many photos during the games too. You like football, right? Which player do you like the most?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Great to hear you watch football every day. Barcelona is a fun team to follow. Which Indian player do you enjoy watching the most?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like watching Sandesh Jhingan play for India. He is very strong and good at defending. Also, I love how he celebrates after a goal, it makes me smile. Sometimes I take photos of my friends playing local matches, I think it's fun. Do you play any sport, or only watch?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Sandesh Jhingan’s celebrations are a joy to watch. Taking photos of friends’ matches sounds fun. Do you play any sport yourself?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I used to play football a lot when I was in school, but now it's mostly watching. Sometimes I play with friends in the park, but not as much as I want. I miss scoring goals! Oh, and I also like taking photos during the game — it's like keeping a memory. You ever play football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, scoring goals sure feels amazing. Taking photos during games is a great way to keep memories. Do you take photos from the field or just from the stands?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mostly from the stands, but sometimes I go closer to the field if I can. I try to capture the players' expressions, you know? It's like telling a story through photos. But I miss playing... maybe I should start again. It's lonely just watching sometimes. Oh well, I should get back to studying for the Bank exam. Talk to you later!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Capturing players’ expressions sounds like a real story in itself. Playing again could be a great break from studying. Which part of the Bank exam are you focusing on now?\""
    }
  ],
